  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240°C/ 220°C (fan)/ gas 9</p><p>Slice the <strong>basa fillets</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>Slice each half into 3 pieces (roughly the size and shape of fish fingers) so that you are left with 12 <span class=\"text-danger\">[24]</span> fish fingers</p><p>Add the <strong>curry powder</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a plate with the fish<strong> </strong>fingers and coat them in the spices</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1133.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1133.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1133.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1133.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1133.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a separate plate</p><p>Crack the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into a bowl and beat with a fork</p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to another plate</p><p>Coat the <strong>fish fingers</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add them to the <strong>beaten egg</strong>, finally press them firmly into the <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> until evenly coated</p><p>Add the <strong>breaded</strong> <strong>fish fingers</strong> to a plate and pop them in the fridge until later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1133.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
