            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Cut the<strong> potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 10-15 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once done, drain, set aside and reserve the pot for later</p>",
