    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice the<strong> brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>mayo</strong> with the<strong> mango chutney </strong>in a small bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>mango mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
