      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the<strong> blanched peas</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min or until tender</p><p>Once tender, drain the <strong>peas</strong> and return them to the pot over a low heat</p><p>Add a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and cook for 1 min further or until melted – these are your <strong>buttery peas</strong></p>",
